Quick Start Example

Create a payment using curl.

curl -X POST https://api.payflowcloud.com/v1/payments \
  -H "Authorization: Bearer sk_live_91dhdh82hdk2hd82h" \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{
    "amount": 5000,
    "currency": "USD",
    "customer_id": "cus_847382",
    "payment_method": "card",
    "description": "Premium subscription"
  }'


Successful response:

{
  "id": "pay_9384723",
  "status": "succeeded",
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "USD"
}

Your application can now store the payment ID and confirm the transaction to the user.


